627
00:59:59,952 --> 01:00:01,033
[SPEAKER_01]: There we are.

628
01:00:03,215 --> 01:00:03,575
[SPEAKER_01]: There we go.

629
01:00:03,856 --> 01:00:07,579
[SPEAKER_01]: So, and with the community gardens here in the center.

630
01:00:07,599 --> 01:00:21,594
[SPEAKER_01]: The transmission line work was, there was a lay down yard in this area around this leg of the proposed path here where there was material stored and this is where the transmission line work was taking place for the underground work.

631
01:00:23,680 --> 01:00:35,465
[SPEAKER_01]: And so what we're looking to do is have a, sorry, as part of the mitigation, have a bike path installed here from the intersection down through to the existing bike path, Mystic Valley Path, here along the river.

632
01:00:36,365 --> 01:00:50,091
[SPEAKER_01]: We also, in discussions with the town and DCR and some other entities, also requested that this leg down here be added to connect to the existing crosswalk here at Winthrop Street, north of the bridge, to the existing path.

633
01:00:50,912 --> 01:00:58,199
[SPEAKER_01]: There is already actually, as you can see here, and I have some photos as well, there is some high wear from people already cutting across this area.

634
01:00:58,560 --> 01:00:59,381
[SPEAKER_01]: It's quite wide.

635
01:00:59,401 --> 01:01:03,805
