636
01:01:04,366 --> 01:01:06,768
[SPEAKER_01]: So what we're proposing are those two legs of the path.

637
01:01:07,409 --> 01:01:11,171
[SPEAKER_01]: as well as up top installing ADA compliant crosswalks at the corners.

638
01:01:11,211 --> 01:01:22,097
