682
01:06:05,150 --> 01:06:07,211
[SPEAKER_01]: We don't expect this to impact flood storage.

683
01:06:07,231 --> 01:06:12,815
[SPEAKER_01]: We're not expecting to restrict flows or impair the ability of the area to provide its current level of habitat function.

684
01:06:13,235 --> 01:06:18,338
