686
01:06:26,371 --> 01:06:31,212
[SPEAKER_01]: And then the race crosswalk and the ADA compliant crosswalks are already in paved roadway.

687
01:06:31,252 --> 01:06:40,554
[SPEAKER_01]: So we're hoping that we find those under the Wetland Protection Act as an exempt minor activity for resurfacing and repair of an existing paved roadway.

688
